{"tid":225194,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日落bar蒲飲大左，比契哥搞左","createTime":"2017-05-01T15:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T16:57:56.000Z","uid":44035,"like":4,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6802b865d27463e436bed4bbfe08c60951479150","tid":225194,"uid":44035,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:11:43.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 琴日完左sem暪住男朋友同成班人落bar蒲<br />\n<br />\n後尾飲到好wing又想嘔<br />\n契哥截的士送我返屋企<br />\n<br />\n我仲醉緊既時候佢帶左我去後樓梯<br />\n原本係幫我掃背脊<br />\n後尾feel到佢解左我bra帶<br />\n係咁從後揸我波又掃我lin頭<br />\n搞到我好high仲濕左 <br />\n後尾佢插左入黎 我有話唔好 我有男朋友<br />\n佢唔理 發左癲咁屌我<br />\n但佢條野真係大過我男朋友 有少少爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後佢仲射曬入黎....<br />\n<br />\n我男朋友成日都叫我唔好同佢行咁埋 話佢個樣好狗公 咸咸濕濕咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我冇理到佢仲話佢痴綠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家覺得好對唔住男朋友 仲好驚唔知會唔會有BB <br />\n點算好 應唔應該坦白同佢講 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1536ccdc915db642b6899283e6871da15a2a6f3","tid":225194,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:13:05.000Z","msg":"Pm我幫幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb4ce2536956e57cbecb1d1ca6ac432682a38c1","tid":225194,"uid":28237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:13:43.000Z","msg":"諗起潮文"},{"pid":"bd193e0a77e514a02e294b571dddfbaf0391a4fe","tid":225194,"uid":6783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/01/231336_fca91f44b8b7031113b19f05dfc0b225.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F01%2F231336_f